name: FanMuseJobs
0:
”Alexa, ask fan muse jobs to give me the newest job postings”
”Alexa, ask fan muse jobs to tell me jobs near New York City Metro Area”
”Alexa, ask fan muse jobs to show jobs that are Entry Level”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: fan muse jobs
des:
The purpose of this skill is to find the newest job postings from themuse.com. To start, enable the skill. Once linked you may now go ahead and use it with starting with "Alexa, launch fan muse jobs.". You can find jobs based on location, based on experience level, and based on category.

This skill is not sponsored or endorsed by themuse. 
This skill is not sponsored or endorsed by Daily Muse, Inc.
This skill is not sponsored or endorsed by Amazon.

Any questions or feedback about the skill email me at: antonio.cucciniello16@gmail.com

Check out the code for the skill here: https://github.com/acucciniello/the-muse-jobs

Check out videos of the skill working here: https://acucciniello.github.io/the-muse-jobs/
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
